# Reusable package repo ignore baseline

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# OS/editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs and local run artifacts
**/logs/
**/results/runs/
**/results/prereq/

# Generated exports and bulky outputs
**/reports/*_FINAL_*.md
**/reports/EXECUTIVE_SUMMARY_*.md
**/reports/FINDINGS_*.md
**/reports/REMEDIATION_*.md
**/reports/BUNDLE_NOTES_*.md
**/reports/*.html
**/reports/*.pdf
**/slides/SLIDES_*.md
**/slides/*.pptx

# Optional evidence / generated artifacts
**/evidence/

# Local git helper leftovers
*.orig
